OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,FThe government should consider a
OL,7,F"total ban" on commercial sunbeds, a
OL,8,Fcommittee of senior advisors has urged
OL,9,Fministers, amid reports of increased
OL,10,Fpopularity of the products among young
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FThe new report from the Committee on
OL,14,FMedical Aspects of Radiation in the
OL,15,FEnvironment (Comare), which is
OL,16,Fadvising the government on the health
OL,17,Feffects of radiation, says that sunbed
OL,18,Fuse has "not been much reduced,
OL,19,Fdespite the introduction of laws to
OL,20,Fcontrol use".
OL,26,@zD@IOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,FIt says that there are also
OL,7,Fsuggestions that young people are
OL,8,F"increasingly" using them.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, some sunbed operators are
OL,11,Fusing social media to make "false and
OL,12,Funsubstantiated claims of health
OL,13,Fbenefits" of sunbeds, the new report
OL,14,Fstates.
OL,16,FThe experts recommend that the
OL,17,Fgovernment should "consider whether it
OL,18,Fis appropriate to introduce a complete
OL,19,Fban on the commercial use of sunbeds".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]sD@\OUuD@IO]yD@SOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
