OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,FSunbeds use high-intensity ultraviolet
OL,7,F(UV) radiation for tanning.
OL,9,FComare is a senior group of
OL,10,Findependent advisors who work within
OL,11,Fthe government to give advice on the
OL,12,Fhealth effects of natural and human-
OL,13,Fmade radiation.
OL,15,FCancer Research UK says there is "no
OL,16,Fsuch thing as safe UV tanning" and too
OL,17,Fmuch UV radiation from the sun or
OL,18,Fsunbeds causes skin cancer.
OL,26,@wD@bOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,FLeading skin doctors from the British
OL,7,FAssociation of Dermatologists and the
OL,8,FBritish Photodermatology Group have
OL,9,Fcalled for a complete ban on
OL,10,Fcommercial sunbeds.
OL,12,FSince 2010 it has been illegal for
OL,13,Fchildren to use sunbeds.
OL,15,FBut the new report states: "The
OL,16,Fnumbers of commercial sunbed outlets
OL,17,Fin the UK do not appear to have
OL,18,Fdeclined appreciably since 2009,
OL,19,Fsuggesting that use has also not been
OL,20,Fmuch reduced, despite the introduction
OL,21,Fof laws to control use.
OL,26,@wD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,F"There are also indications of
OL,7,Fincreasing use by young people."
OL,9,FThe authors add: "Some sunbed
OL,10,Foperators are making false and
OL,11,Funsubstantiated claims of health
OL,12,Fbenefits and this is reinforced by the
OL,13,Fprevalence of such misinformation on
OL,14,Fsocial media platforms."
OL,16,FThey recommend that the government
OL,17,Fshould revisit 2009 recommendations to
OL,18,Fcontrol sunbed use.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@`O]qD@ROUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,FComare also call for the government to
OL,7,Fconsider a total ban which "may be
OL,8,Fconsidered a legitimate course of
OL,9,Faction".
OL,11,F"Government will also wish to consider
OL,12,Fwhether it is appropriate to introduce
OL,13,Fa complete ban on the commercial use
OL,14,Fof sunbeds," the authors wrote.
OL,26,@oD@\OUqD@GO]sD@AOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,F"While a ban should save lives and
OL,7,Freduce costs of cancer treatment,
OL,8,Fthere are wider policy considerations,
OL,9,Ffor example in relation to the
OL,10,Fconstraint on freedom of individual
OL,11,Fchoice, which applies to a range of
OL,12,Fself-imposed risks.
OL,14,F"If government opts for a ban, this
OL,15,Fwill require careful planning, with
OL,16,Fsupporting public awareness campaigns
OL,17,Fand strong enforcement."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
