OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780945878
OL,3,CMajor report recommends complete ban
OL,4,Con sunbeds
OL,6,F"Sunbed operators have demonstrated
OL,7,Fthat they are not able to consistently
OL,8,Fmeet existing requirements, including
OL,9,Flimits on the amount of UV radiation
OL,10,Femitted by their machines and age
OL,11,Frestrictions."
OL,13,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,14,FCare has been approached for comment.
